label: A2B5_mC28_15_f_e2f-003
title: $\zeta$-Nb$_{2}$O$_{5}$ (B-Nb$_{2}$O$_{5}$) Structure
comments:
This structure is referred to as both $\zeta$-Nb$_{2}$O$_{5}$ and B-Nb$_{2}$O$_{5}$. 
 Nb$_{2}$O$_{5}$ and \href{current_web_home_dir/A2B5_mC28_15_f_e2f-001}{B$_{2}$Pd$_{5}$} share the same AFLOW prototype label, A2B5\_mC28\_15\_f\_e2f, but have substantially different environments around each atom.  The structures are generated by the same symmetry operations with different sets of parameters ({\tt --params}) specified in their corresponding CIF files. 
 Previously (Hicks, 2021) we inadvertantly set $y_{1} = 0.6465$.  The correct value is 0.8965. 
 The ICSD uses Sb$_{2}$O$_{5}$ as the prototype for this structure.
